"Scans every wallet's maildir/inbox/{new,cur} for AXIOM/error/* .eml files. For each: shows the validator handle (From), timestamp, error code extracted from the base64 body (E_* token via byte-scan, no full CBOR decode), and the AXIOM/error/<uuid> subject. No file is modified or deleted. The kiddo-cheque-drop investigation needs this to distinguish transport-drops (no .eml at all) from validator rejections (.eml with AXIOM/error subject + extractable error code)." = "掃描所有錢包的 maildir/inbox/{new,cur},尋找 AXIOM/error/* .eml 檔案。每一個都會顯示驗證者代號 (From)、時間戳記、從 base64 內容擷取的錯誤碼 (透過位元組掃描取得 E_* 字串,不做完整 CBOR 解碼),以及 AXIOM/error/<uuid> 主旨。不會修改或刪除任何檔案。kiddo-cheque-drop 調查需要此功能來區分傳輸丟包 (完全沒有 .eml) 與驗證者拒絕 (具有 AXIOM/error 主旨與可擷取錯誤碼的 .eml)。";
"Scans the wallets directory for stale locks, orphaned pair registrations, unreadable wallet.cbor files, and partial pairs. Read-only — auto-fixes are explicit per-row clicks." = "掃描錢包目錄,尋找過期的鎖定、孤立的錢包對註冊、無法讀取的 wallet.cbor 檔案,以及不完整的錢包對。唯讀 — 自動修復需逐列明確點擊。";
"Scarred FACT links" = "已損傷的 FACT 連結";
"Scars" = "損傷";
"Schedule for later — coming in a follow-up." = "排程稍後執行 — 將於後續更新中提供。";
