"Sends, receives, redeems, heals, and burns appear here as you make them. Each row is signed off-chain by the SDK and recorded locally — no network call needed to display." = "您所進行的發送、接收、兌領、修復與燒毀都會顯示於此。每一列都由 SDK 於鏈下簽署並記錄於本機 — 顯示時不需要網路呼叫。";
"Set during onboarding. Defaults to a different password from your first pair's wallet key — change it here if you want to share or rotate it." = "在導覽期間設定。預設與您第一個錢包對的密鑰不同 — 若想共用或輪替,可在此變更。";
