"Settings → Network → ‘Refresh seeds from axiom-dist’ forces a re-pull. Auto-refreshes when remote SEEDS_VERSION > cached." = "設定 → 網路 → 「從 axiom-dist 重新整理種子」可強制重新拉取。當遠端的 SEEDS_VERSION 大於快取時會自動重新整理。";
