"Some issues remain. Heal again later — CLARA TX_HEAL may need Nabla gossip to converge first." = "仍有問題未解決。請稍後再次修復 — CLARA TX_HEAL 可能需要等待 Nabla gossip 先收斂。";
"Standard" = "標準";
