"TYPE" = "類型";
"Terminates the Kiddo process (if running) and removes Kiddo's accounts.json. Keychain entries are left in place (cross-app keychain delete needs an entitlement this build doesn't have under ad-hoc signing) — they become orphaned UUIDs that don't tie back to any account, and don't interfere with a fresh Kiddo setup. Use `Keychain Access.app` to remove them manually if desired." = "終止 Kiddo 處理程序 (若在執行中) 並移除 Kiddo 的 accounts.json。鑰匙圈項目會保留 (跨應用程式的鑰匙圈刪除需要此版本在 ad-hoc 簽名下未具備的權利 entitlement) — 它們會成為不再對應任何帳號的孤立 UUID,不會干擾全新的 Kiddo 設定。如想手動移除,請使用「鑰匙圈存取.app」。";
"The app password unlocks the login screen. Changing it does not affect any wallet's signing key." = "應用程式密碼用於解鎖登入畫面。變更它不會影響任何錢包的簽署金鑰。";
"The fingerprint above is BLAKE3 over the two anchors below. The anchors are the actual key material the protocol trusts; the fingerprint is the convenient hash. Auditors and operators can compare these against the Yellow Paper §G1 listing." = "上方的指紋是下方兩個錨點的 BLAKE3 雜湊。錨點才是協定真正信任的金鑰素材;指紋只是方便對照的雜湊。稽核員與操作員可將其與 Yellow Paper §G1 清單比對。";
"The most recent Nabla TARDIS tick this wallet observed. Captured on register ops (genesis claim, send, heal) — the wallet does not poll Nabla continuously (YPX-002). The +<time> suffix counts wall-clock seconds since that observation; it persists across app relaunches via UserDefaults." = "此錢包觀察到的最新 Nabla TARDIS tick。會在註冊操作 (起始領取、發送、修復) 時擷取 — 錢包不會持續輪詢 Nabla (YPX-002)。+<time> 字尾表示自該次觀察以來經過的實際秒數;會透過 UserDefaults 在應用程式重啟後保留。";
"The source is open. The cryptography is public. The rules are meant to be examined, verified, and challenged. What you cannot verify, you should not believe — including this." = "原始碼是開放的。密碼學是公開的。規則本就應該被檢視、驗證與挑戰。無法驗證的事物,您就不該相信 — 包括這段話本身。";
"The wallet picks validators advertising your preferred carriers, top to bottom. Email is always at the bottom — every validator advertises it (YP §27.5.2), and the wallet falls back to email-only when it can't form a witness round on your preferred carriers." = "錢包會由上至下挑選宣告您偏好載具的驗證者。電子郵件永遠在最底層 — 每個驗證者都會宣告 (YP §27.5.2),當錢包無法在您偏好的載具上組成見證回合時,會退回到僅使用電子郵件。";
"The wallet refuses to open without a functional SDK runtime — broadcast operations would fail mid-flight otherwise." = "若 SDK 執行時無法正常運作,錢包會拒絕開啟 — 否則廣播操作將在中途失敗。";
"There is no central ledger deciding reality for everyone else. There is no authority to petition. Transactions are witnessed by independent validators. Value is redeemed only when the recipient chooses to redeem it. Consensus emerges from observation, not authority." = "沒有任何中央帳本替所有人決定現實。沒有可以申訴的權威機構。交易由獨立的驗證者見證。價值只有在收款方選擇兌領時才會兌領。共識源自觀察,而非權威。";
"There is no support line. The secrets above are the only copy. Save them, then confirm below." = "沒有客服專線。上方的機密是唯一的副本。請妥善保存,然後於下方確認。";
"This appears on the tab strip." = "此名稱會顯示在分頁列上。";
"This build supports" = "此版本支援";
"This is the default for wallets onboarded before 2026-05-27. Anyone who learns your wallet key (e.g., by watching you type it during a send) can also open the app and browse balance + history. Consider changing your app password to a different string for the shoulder-surf defense." = "這是 2026-05-27 之前完成導覽的錢包的預設值。任何得知您錢包密鑰的人 (例如在您發送時偷看到輸入內容) 也能開啟應用程式並瀏覽餘額與紀錄。建議將應用程式密碼變更為不同字串,以防偷窺。";
"This is the password you set when installing the wallet. It unlocks your wallet pairs." = "這是您安裝錢包時設定的密碼,用於解鎖您的錢包對。";
"This is the world you have been given." = "這就是被交給您的世界。";
"This new pair will be a completely separate wallet — different keys, different wallet_id (per-pair salt and hex), different balance, different transaction history. Sharing the email is just a contact label; the two pairs cannot see each other's funds." = "此新錢包對會是完全獨立的錢包 — 不同的金鑰、不同的 wallet_id (每對各自的 salt 與 hex)、不同的餘額、不同的交易紀錄。共用電子郵件只是聯絡標籤;兩個錢包對無法看到彼此的資金。";
"This pair has no Ark companion on disk — only the Normal mode backup is required." = "此錢包對在磁碟上沒有 Ark 伴侶 — 僅需 Normal 模式的備份。";
"This system does not ask for permission." = "此系統不會請求許可。";
"This transaction will be significantly slower because " = "此筆交易會明顯較慢,因為 ";
"This wallet talks to validators and Nabla ONLY through the SDK's exposed FFI. No direct URLSession to validator endpoints. No direct TCP socket to Nabla nodes. KIDDO (the SDK's SMTP client) is the carrier for everything. Every cell of UI data comes from the FFI surface." = "此錢包僅透過 SDK 公開的 FFI 與驗證者及 Nabla 溝通。不會直接以 URLSession 連線驗證者端點。不會直接以 TCP socket 連線 Nabla 節點。所有傳輸都由 KIDDO (SDK 的 SMTP 用戶端) 擔任載具。介面上的每一格資料都來自 FFI 介面。";
"Three destructive operations behind a passcode: clear the audit log of processed cheques for the active wallet, clear EVERY wallet's maildir + outbox + cheques on this Mac, and reset AxiomKiddo (terminate process + remove accounts.json). Each ack independently. Wrong passcode dismisses silently." = "三個位於密碼後的破壞性操作:清除啟用中錢包已處理支票的稽核紀錄、清除此 Mac 上所有錢包的 maildir + outbox + 支票,以及重設 AxiomKiddo (終止處理程序 + 移除 accounts.json)。每一項各自確認。密碼錯誤時會靜默關閉。";
"Three operations, in increasing destructiveness. Each has its own ack checkbox so you can use one without arming the others." = "三項操作,破壞性逐步遞增。每一項都有獨立的確認核取方塊,讓您可以單獨使用而不啟用其他項目。";
"Three options. The first preserves your wallets and history if you have your Wallet Secret backup from onboarding; the other two are last resorts." = "三個選項。若您持有導覽期間的錢包機密備份,第一項可保留錢包與紀錄;另外兩項則是最後手段。";
