"Total supply (cap)" = "總供應量 (上限)";
"Treasury" = "金庫";
"Tried in order — first carrier is preferred (YP §26.9.3)." = "依序嘗試 — 第一個載具優先 (YP §26.9.3)。";
"Trust belongs to the mesh, not to its founders." = "信任屬於網路本身,而非其創始者。";
"Two secrets — one per wallet. Lose them and the money locked behind them is unrecoverable. Save them somewhere offline before continuing." = "兩個機密 — 每個錢包一個。一旦遺失,被它們鎖住的資金將無法救回。請先離線保存後再繼續。";
